        "title": "メンバーを新規登録する",
        "text": "\n\nプロジェクト一覧 ＞ 3333 ＞メンバーを新規登録する\n\n\n\t3333メンバー新規登録\n\n\n\n1. ユーザの検索\n\t \t \t\n2. プロジェクトへ登録するメンバーの選択\t\n\n \t \t \t \n \t \t \t※ユーザ選択、権限設定後、[新規登録]押下しメンバー登録されます。\n\n※検索項目を入力し、ユーザを検索してください。\n\t \t \t \n \t \t \t\nチェックしたユーザを\t\n一括操作\n\tする\t\n\t\t\n\n \t \t \t \n \t \t \t全チェック   全チェック解除\n\nユーザ名\t\nディビジョン名\t\nサブディビジョンID\t\nサブディビジョン名\t\n\n\n検索結果は、最大上位1000件を表示します。\n1000件以上ヒットした場合、条件を絞り込んでください。\n\t \t \t\n 　 \tユーザ\tレベル\n\n",
        "dom": "<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"ja\"><head>\n<meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=11\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"css/default2.css\" type=\"text/css\">\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"script/UserAgent.js\" charset=\"UTF-8\"></script><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<title>メンバーを新規登録する</title>\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n<!--\nINPUT {ime-mode:active;}\n-->\n</style>\n<!--プロジェクトメンバー新規登録-->\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"script/PatlicsMessage.js\" charset=\"UTF-8\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"script/ItemDefine_ja.js\" charset=\"UTF-8\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"script/Define.js\" charset=\"UTF-8\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"script/CommonSubWinClose.js\" charset=\"UTF-8\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"script/StrutsValidator.js\" charset=\"UTF-8\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"Javascript1.1\"> \n\n<!-- Begin \n\n     var bCancel = false; \n\n    function validateProjectMemberSearchInsertForm(form) {                                                                   \n        if (bCancel) \n      return true; \n        else \n       return validateMaxLength(form) && validateApproveWord(form); \n   } \n\n    function maxlength () { \n     this.aa = new Array(\"userIdSearch\", \"ユーザID は 64 文字以内にしてください\", new Function (\"varName\", \"this.maxlength='64';  return this[varName];\"));\n    } \n\n    function approveWord () { \n     this.aa = new Array(\"userIdSearch\", \"ユーザID で使用できない文字が入力されています\", new Function (\"varName\", \"this.reserve='ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789@.-_$&?*!%';  return this[varName];\"));\n    } \n\n\n//End --> \n</script>\n\n<script>\n<!--\n\nvar rFlag = true;\nvar msgFlag = false;\nvar color_blueA = \"#4275D6\";\nvar color_blueB = \"#99ccff\";\nvar color_redA  = \"#D64275\";\nvar color_redB  = \"#ff9999\";\nvar color_grayA = \"#777777\";\nvar color_grayB = \"#b5b5b5\";\nvar color_grayC = \"#dddddd\";\nvar color_grayD = \"#eeeeee\";\n\nfunction setLinkTD(elmt, bol, kind){\n\tif(bol){\n\t\tif(kind == \"doc\"){\n\t\t\telmt.style.backgroundColor = color_blueA;\n\t\t}else if(kind == \"eval\"){\n\t\t\telmt.style.backgroundColor = color_redA;\n\t\t}\n\t\telmt.style.color = \"#ffffff\";\n\t}else{\n\t\tif(kind == \"doc\"){\n\t\t\telmt.style.backgroundColor = color_grayD;\n\t\t}else if(kind == \"eval\"){\n\t\t\telmt.style.backgroundColor = color_redB;\n\t\t}\n\t\telmt.style.color = \"#000000\";\n\t}\n}\n\nvar blocFlag = false;\nfunction dispBlocCtrl(bol){\n\tif(bol == null){\n\t\tblocFlag = true;\n\t\treturn;\n\t}\n\tif(bol){\n\t\tblocFlag = bol;\n\t\tvar disp_d = document.all('blocMenu').style.display;\n\t\tif(disp_d == \"none\"){\n\t\t\tdocument.all('blocTb').style.borderStyle = \"inset\";\n\t\t\tdocument.all('blocTb').style.backgroundColor=\"#9292ac\";\n\t\t\tdocument.all('blocMenu').style.display='block';\n\t\t}else{\n\t\t\tdocument.all('blocTb').style.borderStyle = \"outset\";\n\t\t\tdocument.all('blocTb').style.backgroundColor=\"#d2d2ec\";\n\t\t\tdocument.all('blocMenu').style.display='none';\n\t\t}\n\t\treturn;\n\t}else if(!blocFlag && document.all('blocMenu')){\n\t\tdocument.all('blocMenu').style.display='none';\n\t}\n\tblocFlag = false;\n}\n\nfunction focusBlocCtrl(elmt, focus){\n\tif(focus){\n\t\t\telmt.style.borderColor=color_grayB;\n\t\t\telmt.style.backgroundColor=\"#d2d2ec\";\n\t}else{\n\t\t\telmt.style.borderColor=color_grayC;\n\t\t\telmt.style.borderStyle = \"outset\";\n\t\t\telmt.style.backgroundColor = \"#d2d2ec\";\n\t}\n}\n\nfunction setChkItemsAll(setting){\n\tvar lId;\n\tif(document.forms[0].addProjectMember){\n\t\tif(setting == true){\n\t\t\tif(document.forms[0].addProjectMember.length){\n\t\t\t\tvar proMem = document.forms[0].addProjectMember;\n\t\t\t\tfor(var i = 0; i < proMem.length; i++){\n\t\t\t\t\tif(proMem[i].disabled == false){\n\t\t\t\t\t\tproMem[i].checked = true;\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t} else {\n\t\t\t\tif(document.forms[0].addProjectMember.disabled == false){\n\t\t\t\t\tdocument.forms[0].addProjectMember.checked = true;\n\t\t\t\t} else {\n\t\t\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}else{\n\t\t\tif(document.forms[0].addProjectMember.length){\n\t\t\t\tvar proMem = document.forms[0].addProjectMember;\n\t\t\t\tfor(var i = 0; i < proMem.length; i++){\n\t\t\t\t\tif(proMem[i].disabled == false){\n\t\t\t\t\t\tproMem[i].checked = false;\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t} else {\n\t\t\t\tif(document.forms[0].addProjectMember.disabled == false){\n\t\t\t\t\tdocument.forms[0].addProjectMember.checked = false;\n\t\t\t\t} else {\n\t\t\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t}else{\n\t\treturn;\n\t}\n}\n\nfunction updateType(selectType){\n\tvar checkInfo = document.forms[0].addProjectMember;\n\tif(checkInfo){\n\t\tvar checkLen = checkInfo.length;\n\t\tvar checkCount = 0;\n\t\tfor(var i = 0; i < checkLen; i++){\n\t\t\tif(checkInfo[i].checked == true){\n\t\t\t\tcheckCount++;\n\t\t\t} \n\t\t}\n\t\tif(checkInfo.checked == true){\n\t\t\t\tcheckCount++;\n\t\t}\n\t\tif(checkCount == 0){\n\t\t\talert(\"チェックがありません。\");\n\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t}\n\t\tif(checkLen){\n\t\t\tfor(var i = 0; i < checkLen; i++){\n\t\t\t\tif(checkInfo[i].checked == true){\n\t\t\t\t\tif(selectType == \"0\"){\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdocument.all(\"type\"+i).innerHTML = \"管理者\";\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdocument.forms[0].levelSelect[i].value = selectType;\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t\tif(selectType == \"3\"){\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdocument.all(\"type\"+i).innerHTML = \"編集メンバー\";\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdocument.forms[0].levelSelect[i].value = selectType;\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t\tif(selectType == \"6\"){\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdocument.all(\"type\"+i).innerHTML = \"一般メンバー\";\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdocument.forms[0].levelSelect[i].value = selectType;\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t\tif(selectType == \"9\"){\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdocument.all(\"type\"+i).innerHTML = \"閲覧メンバー\";\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdocument.forms[0].levelSelect[i].value = selectType;\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t} else {\n\t\t\tif(checkInfo.checked == true){\n\t\t\t\tif(selectType == \"0\"){\n\t\t\t\t\tdocument.all(\"type0\").innerHTML = \"管理者\";\n\t\t\t\t\tdocument.forms[0].levelSelect.value = selectType;\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\tif(selectType == \"3\"){\n\t\t\t\t\tdocument.all(\"type0\").innerHTML = \"編集メンバー\";\n\t\t\t\t\tdocument.forms[0].levelSelect.value = selectType;\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\tif(selectType == \"6\"){\n\t\t\t\t\tdocument.all(\"type0\").innerHTML = \"一般メンバー\";\n\t\t\t\t\tdocument.forms[0].levelSelect.value = selectType;\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\tif(selectType == \"9\"){\n\t\t\t\t\tdocument.all(\"type0\").innerHTML = \"閲覧メンバー\";\n\t\t\t\t\tdocument.forms[0].levelSelect.value = selectType;\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t} else {\n\t\talert(\"変更対象がありません。\");\n\t\treturn;\n\t}\n}\n\nfunction searchMember(url, form){\n\n\ttargetForm = eval(\"document.\" + form);\n\tif (!validateProjectMemberSearchInsertForm(targetForm)) {\n\t\treturn;\n\t}\n\n\t\n\tvar userNameSearch=null;\t\t//ユーザ名\n\tvar userIdSearch=null;\t\t\t//ユーザID\n\tvar userDivisionNameSearch=null;//ディビジョン名\n\tvar userDivisionIdSearch=null;\t//ディビジョンID\n\tvar userCommentSearch=null;\t\t//コメント\n\tvar userMailSearch=null;\t\t//メール\n\t\n\t// ユーザ名\n\tuserNameSearch=document.forms[0].userNameSearch.value;\n\t// ユーザID\n\tuserIdSearch=document.forms[0].userIdSearch.value;\n\t//ディビジョン名\n\tuserDivisionNameSearch=document.forms[0].userDivisionNameSearch.value;\n\t//ディビジョンID\n\tuserDivisionIdSearch=document.forms[0].userDivisionIdSearch.value;\n\t//コメント\n\tuserCommentSearch=document.forms[0].userCommentSearch.value;\n\t//メール\n\tuserMailSearch=document.forms[0].userMailSearch.value;\n\t//サブディビジョンID\n\tvar userSubDivisionIdSearch=document.forms[0].userSubDivisionIdSearch.value;\n\t//サブディビジョン名\n\tvar userSubDivisionNameSearch=document.forms[0].userSubDivisionNameSearch.value;\n\t\n\tif ((userIdSearch==null || userIdSearch==\"\" ) &&\n\t\t(userNameSearch==null || userNameSearch==\"\" ) && \n\t\t(userDivisionNameSea